on"><Data ss:Type="String">5. Custom-made products are non-refundable once production has started.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Section"><Data ss:Type="String">6. Freight cost may change if final CBM, weight, or delivery address changes.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Section"><Data ss:Type="String">7. Any customs duties, import taxes, or local charges are subject to the agreed trade term.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Section"><Data ss:Type="String">8. Minor color variation may occur due to material batches, lighting, and screen display differences.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Section"><Data ss:Type="String">9. Warranty terms apply to normal commercial use only. Damage caused by misuse, improper installation, or transportation handling is not covered unless otherwise agreed.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Section"><Data ss:Type="String">10. This Proforma Invoice becomes valid after buyer confirmation and deposit payment.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Section"><Data ss:Type="String">SIGNATURES</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Prepared By</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jordan Lee</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Approved By</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Company Representative / Signature</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Buyer Confirmation</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Name / Signature / Date</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Company Stamp</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell></Row></Table></Worksheet></Workbook>